dct_title_s: [Kharitat al-Iraq]: Nahiyata al-Aziziya wa Salman Pak wa Shubat as-Suwayra
dct_description_sm: Iraq. Mudiriyat al-Masahah al-Ammah. Iraq. Directorate General of Surveys. [[Map of Iraq]: Al-Aziziya, Salman Pak, and Suwayra sections]. Alternate title: Liwa'ay Baghdad wa al-Kut: Qada'ay Baghdad wa al-Kut: Nahiyata al-Aziziya wa Salman Pak wa Shubat as-Suwayra = [Provinces of Baghdad and Al-Kut: Baghdad and Al-Kut districts: Al-Aziziya and Salman Pak sections, with As-Suwayra division.] Relief shown by hachures and form lines. Triangulation points are shown. Surveyed: 1929, 1932. Tribal lands and ownership are shown.
